      "content": "Hey, I'm looking at the latest intel on the border stability in Region X. The briefing notes are a mess—just a bunch of conflicting reports and half-baked sensor data. My client is breathing down my neck for an actual assessment. They don't want a lecture on why the data is bad; they need to know if they should move assets or not. Can you give me a confidence level on whether those borders are going to stay stable? I need a clear, decisive call here.",
